{"tid":1138532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警涉非禮17歲少女被捕","createTime":"2019-05-04T14:57:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T16:22:01.000Z","uid":105678,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c67cce8954ec6a82bb3bcc1727b49b44c9a4655b","tid":1138532,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T14:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190504/s00001/202a1a05d437a8e570819bd8b169de49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190504%2Fs00001%2F202a1a05d437a8e570819bd8b169de49.jpg&h=e941b484&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名17歲少女昨晚（3日）11時許乘小巴至青山公路青龍頭段時，疑遭54歲男子非禮。警方到場調查，發現涉案男子為休班警員，將他拘捕。被捕人已獲准保釋候查，須於5月下旬向警方報到。案件交荃灣警區重案組跟進。<br />\n<br />\n警方強調非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，定必嚴正處理。"},{"pid":"099b400dd31a03f2fa31b61654929cd7d7735e94","tid":1138532,"uid":203657,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T15:00:50.000Z","msg":"對紀律部隊好撚失望"},{"pid":"76e4900a50fb9cac9cfeb57ad707a6b19e9a7b68","tid":1138532,"uid":2748,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T15:01:38.000Z","msg":"54<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56784cfea69780460bc8ceb95b6413dfac1d72c4","tid":1138532,"uid":157362,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T15:02:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38cc2568d7dfdcd2cde8cb1482496533e64a456e","tid":1138532,"uid":294,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T15:03:05.000Z","msg":"初犯, 信耶穌, 紀錄良好, 服務香港<br />\n<br />\n守行為3個月, 停職3個月<br />\n<br />\n3個月後照返工"},{"pid":"f08f14cc9aca6ad548f7b9cf6b7bde0741890dc5","tid":1138532,"uid":209487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T15:04:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd184af7bf964244307d60b58124291a0fee341b","tid":1138532,"uid":200505,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"